column2: selasabeawi mabetoche lamaasetamaare  yamiradu anedaanede zadeewoche.
aneqatse 1;

yasawe leje hulu siwalade natsaanaa bakeberenaa bamabeteme ekulenate yaalawe nawe. yatafatero maasetawaalenaa hhelinaa selaalawe anedu leelaawene bawanedemaamaachenate manefase mamalekate yegabaawaale.
aneqatse 2;

eyaanedaanedu sawe yazare yaqalame yatsotaa yaqwaaneqwaa yahaayemaanote yapolatikaa wayeme yaleelaa aayenate asetasaasabe yabehheeraawi wayeme yaxaberatasabe taarike yahabete yatewelede wayeme yaleelaa darajaa leyunate saayenoru bazihu wesaanee yatazarazarute mabetochenenaa natsaanatoche hulu enedikabarulate yegabaale.

kaziheme bataqara anede sawe kaminorebate agare wayeme gezaate yapolatikaa yaagazaaze wayeme yainetarenaashenaale aqwaame yatanasaa agaru natsaame hona bamogezitenate asetadaadare wayeme eraasune chelo yamaayetadaadare agare tawalaaje bihoneme bamaanenyaaweme aayenate gadabe yaalawe agazaaze sere bihoneme leyunate ayefatsamebateme.
aneqatse 3;
eyaanedaanedu sawe yamanore, banatsaanatenaa basalaame yamanoru matebaqe mabete alawe.
aneqatse 4;
maaneme sawe bihone babaarenate ayegazaame. baarenatenaa yabaariyaa negedeme bamaanenyaaweme aayenate kelekele nawe.
aneqatse 5;
maaneme sawe bihone yachekaanee seqaaye enedaayedaresebate wayeme kasabeaawi afatsaatsame weche yahona yatawaarade tagebaare wayeme qetaate ayefatsamebateme.
aneqatse 6;
eyaanedaanedu sawe bahhege fite basawe zarenatu yamataawaqe mabete alawe.
aneqatse 7;

sawe hulu bahhege fite ekule nawe. yaalaanedaache leyunateme hhegu dahenenatune eneditebaqelate ekule yahona mabete alawe. yehenene wesaanee bamataase kamidarage leyunate lamaaderage kaminasaasaa eneditebaqe hulume yaekule mabete alawe.
aneqatse 8;

eyaanedaanedu sawe bahhega manegesetu wayeme bahhege yatasatutene masarataawi mabetoche kamitesu deregitoche kafetanyaa bahonu behheeraawi yaferede baalaseletaanoche fetsume bahona manegade enediwagadelate mabete alawe.
aneqatse 9;
maaneme sawe yaalaferede tayezo eneditaasare wayeme bagezaate enedinore ayedarageme.
aneqatse 10;

eyaanedaanedu sawe bamabetochunaa bagedeetaawochu afatsaatsame enedihume bamikasasebate maanenyaaweme aayenate yawanejale kese natsaa bahonanaa bamaayaadaalaa yaferede shanego batekekelanyaanaa bayefaa gudaayu enedisamaalate yamulu ekulenate mabete alawe.
aneqatse 11;

bawanejale kese yatakasasa maanenyaaweme sawe lamakalaakayaawe asefalaagiwoche yahonutene hulu aqerebo bamikaraakarebate yayefaa ferede beete bahhege masarate wanejalanyaa mahonu esetiragaagatebate derase kawanejale natsaa enedahona yamaqotere mabete alawe.

maaneme sawe babehheeraawi wayeme bainetarenaashenaale hhege anede nagare wanejale hono baaletadanagagabate gizee bafatsamawe wayeme baalefatsamawe maanenyaaweme seraa wanejalanyaa hono ayekasaseme. wayeme wanejalu batafatsamabate gizee katadanagagawe qetaate yebalete ayefaradebateme.
aneqatse 12;

maaneme sawe bagele nurowe babeetasabu wesete babeetu wayeme bamitsaatsaafawe dabedaabee baferede yaaletalaya taaleqaa gabenate wayeme keberune yaminakaanaa semune yamiyaagodefe taqaawemo ayefatsamebateme. eyaanedaanedu sawe kaenedazihe yaala taaleqaa gabenate wayeme yamigodaa tagebaare hhege enedikalaakalelate mabete alawe.
aneqatse 13;
eyaanedaanedu sawe bayabehheeraawi wasane kelelu yamazawaawarenaa yamanore natsaanate mabete alawe.
eyaanedaanedu sawe kamaanenyaaweme agare hona karaasu agare wateto enedaganaa wada agaru yamamalase mabete alawe.
aneqatse 14;
eyaanedaanedu sawe kacheqonaa shasheto baleeloche agaroche teganyenatene yamateyaqenaa badahenaa yamanore mabete alawe.

polatikaawi kaalehonu wanejaloche wayeme yatabaabarute manegesetaate derejete waanaa aalaamaawochene kamiqaaranu seraawoche yatanasaa bamidaresu kesoche mekeneyaate kahona yehe mabete liyaagalagele ayecheleme.
aneqatse 15;
eyaanedaanedu sawe yazeegenate mabete alawe.
maaneme sawe yaalaferede zeegenatu ayewasadebateme wayeme zeegenatune yamalawate mabete ayenafagaweme.
aneqatse 16;

akaala matene yadarasu wanedochenaa seetoche bazare bazeegenate wayeme bahaayemaanote leyunate saayewasanu gaabechaane yamafatsamenaa beetasabene yamamaserate mabete alaachawe; gaabechaa bamafatsame bagaabechaa gizeenaa gaabechaa bamifaresebateme gizee ekule mabete alaachawe.
gaabechaa yamifatsamawe gaabechaa lamafatsame bamifalegu hulatume waganoche bamiyaadaregute natsaanaa mulu sememenate masarate bechaa nawe.
beetasabe baxabera sabe yatafateronaa masarataawi kefele selahona baxaberasabunaa bamanegesetume dahenenatu eneditebaqelate yegabaale.
aneqatse 17;
eyaanedaanedu sawe bechaawene wayeme kaleeloche gaare baxaberate hono yaxaberate baalabeetenate mabete alawe.
maaneme sawe yaalaferede neberatu ayewasadebateme.
aneqatse 18;

eyaanedaanedu sawe yahaasaabe yahhelinaanaa yahaayemaanote natsaanate mabete alawe. yeheme mabete haayemaanotune wayeme emenatune yamalawate natsaanatenenaa bechaawene wayeme kaleeloche gaare baxaberate bayefaa wayeme bagele hono haayemaanotune wayeme emenatune yamaasetamaare, batagebaare yamagelatse yamaamelakenaa yamaakebare natsaanatene yechameraale.
aneqatse 19;

eyaanedaanedu sawe yahhasaabenaa hhasaabune yamagelatse mabete alawe. yeheme mabete yaalataaleqaa gabenate bahhasaabe yamatsenaatenenaa zeenaane wayeme hhasaabochene yaalaanedaache yadenebare gadabe yamaagenyatene yamaqabalenenaa wayeme yamaakaafalene natsaanateme yechameraale.
aneqatse 20;
eyaanedaanedu sawe basalaame yamasabesabenaa genenyunate yamaaderage natsaanate mabete alawe.
maaneme sawe yaanede maaxabare abaale enedihone ayegadademe.
aneqatse 21;
eyaanedaanedu sawe baqatetaa wayeme natsaa bahona manegade batamaratu enedaraaseewoche amaakaanyenate baagaru manegesete yamakaafale mabete alawe.
eyaanedaanedu sawe baagaru yahezebe agalegelote ekule yamaagenyate mabete alawe.

yamanegesete seletaane masaratu yahhezebu faqaade mahone alabate. yeheme faqaade lahulume ekule bahona bamesetire bamidarage yademetze masetete merechaa wayeme batamasaasaaye huneetaa bayagizeewenaa batekekele bamifatsamu merechaawoche enedigalatse mahone alabate.
aneqatse 22;

eyaanedaanedu sawe yaxabera sabe abaale enedamahonu baxabera sabe dahenenatu eneditebaqe mabete alawe. enedihume babehheeraawi teratenaa bainetarenaashenaale matabaabare amaakaayenatenaa baeyaanedaanedu manegesete derejeteme yahabete menechoche masarate lakeberunaa lasabeaawi aqemu natsaa edegate yagede asefalaagi yahonute yaeekonomi yamaaxabaraawi nuronaa yabaahele mabetoche batagebaare enedigalatsulate mabete alawe.
aneqatse 23;
eyaanedaanedu sawe yamaseraate yaseraa natsaa merechaanaa laseraame tekekelanyaanaa tasemaami yaasaraare huneetaawochenaa seraame enedaayaataa mabete alawe.
eyaanedaanedu sawe yaalaanedaache leyunate maaderage laanede aayenate seraa ekule yahona damawaze yamaagenyate mabete alawe.

baseraa laaye yaala sawe laeraasunaa labeetasabu lasabeaawi kebere tagabi yahona nurone yamiyaaseganyelatenaa kaasefalagame baleeloche yaxaberasabe dahenenate matebaqiyaa zadeewoche yatadagafa tekekelanyaanaa tasemaami waagaawene yamaagenyate mabete alawe.
eyaanedaanedu sawe teqemochune lamaasekabare yamuyaa maaxabarochene lamaaqwaaqwaamenaa maaxabaretanyaa lamahone mabete alawe.
aneqatse 24;
eyaanedaanedu sawe yaerafetenaa yamazenaanaate enedihume baagebaabe yatawasanu yaseraa saaatoche enedinorutenaa bayagizeewe yaerafete gizeeyaatene kadamawaze gaare yamaagenyate mabete alawe.
aneqatse 25;

eyaanedaanedu sawe laeraasunaa labeetasabu teenenatenaa dahenenate megebe, lebese, beetenaa hhekemenaa asefalaagi yamaaxabaraawi nuro agalegelotocheme chemere yamibaqaa yanuro darajaa lamaagenyate mabete alawe. seraa saayeqatere biqare bitaamame lamaseraate baayechele baale wayeme misete bimote biyaaraje wayeme kaquteteru weche bahonu mekeneyaatoche masanaakale bigatemawe dahenenatu eneditebaqelate mabete alawe.

walaadenatenaa hhetsaanenate leyu teneqaaqeenaa eredaataa yamaagenyate mabete alaachawe; bagaabechaa wayeme yaalagaabechaa yamiwaladu hhetsaanaateme yatamasaasaaye yadahenenataachawe matebaqe mabete alaachawe.
aneqatse 26;

eyaanedaanedu sawe yamamaare mabete alawe. temeherete biyaanese biyaanese baanedanyaa darajaanaa bamasarataawi darajaawoche banatsaa lihone yegabaale. yaanedanyaa darajaa temeherete mamaare gedeetaa nawe. yateekenikenaa yaleyu leyu muyaa temeherete bateqelaalaawe yakafetanyaa darajaa dagemo bachelotaa masarate lahulume ekule masatete alabate.

temeherete laeyaanedaanedu sawe huneetaa maashaashaayaanaa lasabeaawi mabetocheme masarataawi natsaanatoche kebere maadaabareyaa yamiwele mahone alabate. enedihume yatalayaaya zare wayeme haayemaanote baalwachawe hhezeboche makaakale hulu magebaabaatene tachaachelo yamanorenenaa yamatabaabarene manefase yamiyaatenakerenaa yatabaabarute manegesetaate derejete salaamene lamatebaqe yamifatsemaachawe tagebaaroche enedisefaafaa yamiyaabarataatu mahone alabate.
walaajoche lalejochaachawe lamasetete yamifalegutene temeherete lamamerate yaqedemiyaa mabete alaachewe.
aneqatse 27;
eyaanedaanedu sawe baxabera sabu yabaahele nuro banatsaa makaafalenaa bakina tebabe lamateqame basaayenese eremejaanaa bateqemochume lamasaatafe mabete alawe.
eyaanedaanedu sawe kadarasawe maanenyaaweme yasaayenese yaderesatenaa yakina tebabe seraa yamiyaaganyawe yamoraalunenaa yahaabete teqemoche enedikabarulate mabete alawe.
aneqatse 28;

eyaanedaanedu sawe bazihe wesaane wesete yatazarazarute mabetochenaa natsaanatoche bamulu batagebaare enediwelu lamidaragebaachawe yaxaberasabenaa yainetarenaashenaale sereaate yamateqame mabete alawe.
aneqatse 29;
eyaanedaanedu sawe yaraasu natsaanatenaa mulu mashaashaale bamiyaaganyebate xaberasabe wesete yamifatsemaachawe gedeetaawoche yenorubataale.

eyaanedaanedu sawe bamabetochu banatsaanatochu bamiteqamebate gizee yamitaagadawe yaleelochene mabetochenaa natsaanatoche bamigabaa lamaasakabare bechaa batadanagagu hhegochenaa yagebera gabenatene yateqelaalaawene hhezebe tzatetaanaa dahenenate badeemokeraatike maaxabaraawi nuro tekekelanyaa yahonawe tafalaagi gudaaye lamaarekaate batawasanawe bechaa nawe.
enazihe mabetochenaa natzaanatoche bamaanenyaaweme huneetaa yatabaabarute manegesetaate derejete masarate aalaamaawoche taqaaraani bahona manegade lifatsamu ayegabaachaweme.
aneqatse 30;

bazihe wesaanee kalaaye yatazarazarawe hulu bazihu wesete yatateqasutene maanaachaweme mabetoche wayeme natsaanatoche lamaabalaashate bataasaba maanenyaaweme aayenate tagebaare lamaawaale wayeme deregitene lamafatsame lamaanenyaaweme manegesete wayeme derejete wayeme sawe yatabaalu ayetaragomume.
